                'Write a query that calculates <code>revenue_per_unit</code> for products in a <code>sales</code> table (columns: <code>product_id</code>, <code>revenue</code>, <code>units_sold</code>). Ensure the query does not crash when <code>units_sold</code> is 0. Use <code>NULLIF</code>. Display <code>product_id</code>, <code>revenue</code>, <code>units_sold</code>, and <code>revenue_per_unit</code>.\n\n---',
